= map-projections
:Author: Rolfe Bozier
:Email: rolfe@pobox.com

Just a simple demo showing how to reproject an image using PROJ.4 into
an Orthographic projection.

Here is an example of the output:

image:aust.png[]

== Prerequisites

You'll need the following to run this script:

The source image:

* http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:WorldMap-A_non-Frame.png

The following perl modules (and their underlying tools):

* Geo::Proj4
* GD

